UPGRADING
=========
Go to the directory of your current TableTop website and run the script
database/backup_database. Make a backup of your current TableTop website.

Replace the entire directory of your current TableTop website with this new
version. Copy the files and directories in public/files from the backup
of your now previous TableTop website to the new version. Change the database
settings in settings/website.conf.

Open https://<your_tabletop_hostname>/setup in your browser and follow the
instructions in your browser to update the database.
